<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٦٤. مِنْ لَامِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فَعْلَى»</span> اسْماً أَتَى الْوَاوُ بَدَلْ … يَاءٍ كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«تَقْوَى»</span>؛ غَالِباً جَا ذَا الْبَدَلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٦٥. بِالْعَكْسِ جَاءَ لَامُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فُعْلَى»</span> وَصْفَا … وَكَوْنُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«قُصْوَى»</span> نَادِراً لَا يَخْفَى<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>